    "question_id" : 4922305,
    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 3.0",
    "body" : "<p>On the Eclipse toolbar, select <em>Window</em> → <em>Preferences</em>, set the font size (<em>General</em> → <em>Appearance</em> → <em>Colors and Fonts</em> → <em>Basic</em> → <em>Text Font</em>).</p>\n\n<p>Save the preferences.</p>\n"
