    "body" : "<p>If you are using STS, then goto STS/Contents/Eclipse directory and open the STS.ini file.</p>\n\n<p>From the STS.ini file, remove the flooring line:</p>\n\n<pre><code>-Dorg.eclipse.swt.internal.carbon.smallFonts\n</code></pre>\n\n<p>And restart the STS.</p>\n"
