    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 4.0",
    "body" : "<p>Press <strong><code>ctrl</code></strong> + <strong><code>-</code></strong> to decrease, and <strong><code>ctrl</code></strong> + <strong><code>+</code></strong> to increase the Font Size.</p>\n<p>It's working for me in Eclipse Oxygen.</p>\n"
